document_data.name: Dunchow
document_data.mainbody: The '''dunchow''' was a rare [[fish]] found only in the waters of [[Lake Esmel]] in [[Amn]]. Dunchow was served as a special dish at most inns in [[Esmeltaran]] and was a delicacy throughout Amn.
